SFTP (From Liximomo)
===================
- Install extention
- Setup sftp Config
    -> Ctrl + Shif + P
    -> Search for SFTP:Config
    -> Set the config like below
    +++ Start Config +++
    {
        "name": "Connection Name",
        "host": "IP/Domain",
        "protocol": "sftp",
        "port": 0000,
        "username": "user_name",
        "remotePath": "path_of_file",
        "uploadOnSave": false
    }
    +++ END CONFIG +++


THEME
=====
One Dark Pro

FONT
====
1. Download font 'Source Code Pro' from internet
2. Install the font on your windows by selecting all .tff file and install
3. Open vscode setting, search for 'font' and inside the font family add 'Source Code Pro' ex : 'Source Code Pro', Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace